column5: Hello i have looked online and there seem to be a decent amount of tackle stores in Hawaii.  I will not be allowed to hit them all, however I will be allowed to go a few.  I don’t really need anything, but it would be nice to go to some stores which have high end equipment and a good selection of everything. is there any input from somebody who has been?  The internet reviews and pics are good intel, but I’d like to hear any personal opinions.  thanks!
Closer to those JDM reels eh?
